title: An Indian on a Tootsie roll.
subtitle: Can the Tootsie Bob rolls of an Indian who shoots an arrow at a star make up for the Tootsie Roll industries for a free bag of candy?
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: The Tootsie Bob cover with an Indian picture of an arrow shooting a star on it that can be replaced by the Tootsie Roll industries for a free candy bag.
